name: Dark Side of the Supermoon
description: Reworking of OBJKT 34624 with a darker twist. The skyline is a real view of uptown São Paulo, Brazil, shot by me. The Moon is from a royalty-free stock photo. Those who know their astronomy will recognize an eclipse is impossible in the manner shown, but in doing so will be skipping the poetic metaphor. First release on #HeNpi, an initiative to price artworks around the number 3.1416. Originally released as HeN OBJKT 147758 on 23 June 2021.
